<node id="A人員">
  <data key="d0">A人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A人员 is an engineer responsible for multiple duties related to system maintenance and customer support. Specifically, they handle the maintenance records for various clients including F客户, B客户, and A客户. On November 24, 2025, A人员 conducted on-site work from 10:30 to 11:00 at F客户的site for system maintenance and was also involved in creating PA monthly reports related to Splunk roles.

A人员's responsibilities extend beyond just record-keeping. They are actively engaged in conducting on-site work at B客户的site, ensuring the smooth operation of B客户’s systems through both direct involvement and remote monitoring. A人员 is one of several engineers tasked with maintaining B客戶's systems, collaborating closely with other team members to address maintenance needs efficiently.

In addition to their duties for F客户 and B客户, A人员 plays a crucial role in maintaining A客户的systems as well. They are responsible for the ongoing upkeep of A客户的infrastructure through regular checks and necessary interventions. This includes being one of several engineers involved in handling the maintenance records for A客戶, ensuring that all activities related to system health and performance are meticulously documented.

Overall, A人员 is integral to the operation and maintenance of multiple clients' systems, providing comprehensive support through a combination of remote monitoring and on-site presence. Their responsibilities include maintaining detailed records, conducting site visits, and collaborating with other engineers to ensure client satisfaction and system reliability.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is an engineer involved in the maintenance process for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance of B客戶's system on 2025/11/06 from 11:00 to 12:00.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is one of the handling engineers for B客户的维护记录.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is one of the engineers involved in handling the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員is an engineer handling the maintenance of B客戶's systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07959bdb8bab221c9c80a1c3e85776b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67cc5a5ed7a1cbea5f9e6d5f5d08ab51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcf7e8f6051fb59b7f2cec85fa4dc4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1364984bd10139c2ef2cd5907a3a7591&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c</data>
