<node id="A部門">
  <data key="d0">A部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A部門is a department within B客戶's organization where specific maintenance activities were carried out, such as adjusting Splunk roles and mailing PA monthly reports.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is an organization within B客戶where maintenance activities took place.&lt;SEP&gt;A部门is a department within an organization where certain maintenance tasks are performed.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is an organization involved in executing specific actions related to B客戶's maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is part of the organization handling maintenance tasks related to Splunk and other system checks.</data>
