<node id="C客戶">
  <data key="d0">C客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">C客戶 is an organization for which detailed maintenance records are systematically documented and kept. The descriptions indicate that Cお客様 has a history of undergoing maintenance activities, with specific documentation related to these services. For instance, on 2026/01/05, B人員 conducted maintenance work for C客户, and this activity was recorded in the organization's maintenance logs. These records serve as an ongoing record of all maintenance activities performed for C客戶, ensuring that historical data is preserved and accessible for future reference.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is an organization for which maintenance records are being processed.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is an organization that had maintenance work recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is a customer who had maintenance work performed on their system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773777785</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="B人員">
  <data key="d0">B人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">B人员 is an engineer responsible for conducting maintenance activities and handling maintenance records for C客户的 systems. The primary role of B人员 includes maintaining the operational integrity and efficiency of C客户's system through various maintenance tasks and ensuring that all necessary documentation related to these activities is accurately recorded and managed.

The descriptions consistently highlight B人员 as a key figure in both performing maintenance work on C客户’s systems and managing records associated with this maintenance. This dual responsibility underscores their role in both the operational aspect and administrative record-keeping of system maintenance for C客户.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the handling engineer responsible for the maintenance of C客户的systems.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer who handled the maintenance for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员is another engineer involved in the maintenance of C客户的system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773777785</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
