<node id="GeoDB">
  <data key="d0">GeoDB</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">GeoDB是一个地理数据库，本周进行了更新。&lt;SEP&gt;GeoDB是一个数据库更新的对象。&lt;SEP&gt;GeoDB is a database that was updated as part of the maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;GeoDB是一个地理数据库，需要进行更新。&lt;SEP&gt;GeoDB是一个地理数据库，本周被更新以进行漏洞修复和其他改进。&lt;SEP&gt;GeoDB is a database that was updated during the maintenance process.&lt;SEP&gt;GeoDB refers to geographical database that was updated during the week's work items.</data>
