<edge source="Splunk Enterprise 10.0.2" target="E客户">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(E客户, Splunk Enterprise 10.0.2) refers to the recommendation for E客户 to upgrade their current version of Splunk Enterprise from an earlier release, specifically version 9.3.8, to version 10.0.2. This upgrade is advised due to several key factors including enhanced security measures and additional feature updates that address recent identified vulnerabilities and weaknesses in previous versions. The transition to version 10.0.2 is aimed at improving system functionality and optimizing performance.

All descriptions highlight the importance of upgrading Splunk Enterprise from version 9.3.8 to the latest version, which includes significant improvements in both security and overall system capabilities. The upgrade is intended to benefit E客户 by ensuring their system stays up-to-date with the latest advancements, thereby enhancing its robustness and reliability. Recommendations are consistent across multiple sources, emphasizing the need for E客戶 to adopt Splunk Enterprise 10.0.2 for optimal performance and security enhancements.&lt;SEP&gt;It is recommended that E客戶upgrade to Splunk Enterprise 10.0.2 due to recent weaknesses found in version 9.3.8.&lt;SEP&gt;The E customer is recommended to upgrade to Splunk Enterprise 10.0.2 due to recent weaknesses and enhanced security features.&lt;SEP&gt;推荐E客户升级至最新版本的Splunk企业版以解决安全问题和性能优化。</data>
  <data key="d9">future compatibility,future version,future_action,future_version,recommended update,recommended_upgrade,recommends_upgrade_to,security enhancement,security improvement,security update,system optimization,upgrade recommendation,upgrade_recommendation,功能增强,安全增强,推荐升级,推荐更新,系统升级建议</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a81645d1d338ac013fa594b14c35640&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9648988cb67db9843bc13754ac3d6ab6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a83bcdf6e7b7269cfd17b4f21457de8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f0773b8daffa7a65254a73867e36afb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d</data>
