<edge source="E客户" target="维护和调整">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(E客户, 维护和调整) conducted multiple maintenance and adjustment tasks in December 2025 to ensure the system's stability, performance, and operational optimization. These activities were part of ongoing system management efforts aimed at keeping the system running smoothly and efficiently throughout the period. The E customer engaged in various maintenance and adjustments during this time, indicating a continuous commitment to managing and improving their system’s functionality and reliability.</data>
  <data key="d9">maintenance,system improvement,system maintenance,system upgrade,update activities,upgrade,upgrade activities</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-726c374f489423e007bce76f7810b46e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6</data>
