</edge>
<edge source="E客户" target="授权用量">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(E客户, 授权用量) is a relation that involves the management of software license quantities and system maintenance requirements. The E client monitors their authorized usage capacity relative to actual system usage, which currently stands at an average of 661.01 GB against a licensed volume of 150 GB. This entity requires continuous monitoring to ensure compliance with authorized usage levels and manage any discrepancies between the allocated license capacity and real-world demand.

In December 2025, E customer underwent several maintenance activities related to adjusting their authorized usage capacity in response to growing system needs. These adjustments were made to align the current license volume more closely with actual system demands, addressing the significant difference between the licensed 150 GB and the average usage of 661.01 GB.

The management of (E客户, 授权用量) also includes proactive measures such as recommendations for expanding authorized capacity to meet future growth requirements. This ensures that the E customer's software licenses remain effective in supporting their system operations efficiently and without constraint.&lt;SEP&gt;The E customer conducted multiple maintenance and adjustment activities in December 2025 related to authorization usage management.</data>
  <data key="d9">adjustment,capacity planning,capacity_management,compliance,license management,licensing,maintenance,maintenance_and_adjustments,monitoring,resource management,resource usage,software licensing,usage compliance,usage monitoring,usage rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-dddcb833d814b293bd936732652206d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-490df5a6810de4f040c4fe2681e6ed6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7</data>
