<edge source="E客户" target="C人员">
  <data key="d7">19.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人员, E客户) describes a relationship where C人员 is responsible for providing various services and support to E客户. Specifically, C人员 executes and coordinates the work related to E客户的 operations, including offering technical support and system optimization services to ensure that E客户's systems are running efficiently. This involves on-site maintenance tasks such as maintaining equipment and troubleshooting issues.

C人员 also handles specific maintenance activities for E客户, which include adjustments in authorization levels and software version upgrades. These collaborative efforts aim at ensuring optimal operation and maintenance of systems used by E客户. C人员 works closely with E客户 to complete several maintenance tasks at the site, demonstrating a strong support and maintenance relationship characterized by continuous collaboration.

On October 30, 2025, C人员 specifically provided maintenance and adjustment services to E客户, illustrating the ongoing nature of this supportive role. Additionally, in December 2025, C人员 continued to provide similar maintenance and adjustment services for E客户的 systems. This partnership is characterized by consistent and effective service delivery, emphasizing the importance of continuous support and collaborative efforts between C人员 and E客户.

Overall, the relationship between C人员 and E客户 involves multiple aspects of system management, including technical support, on-site maintenance, software upgrades, and authorization adjustments. These activities are carried out collaboratively to ensure that E客户的 systems remain operational and efficient over time.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员为E客户提供维护和技术支持，处理其系统优化和功能更新。&lt;SEP&gt;E客户的维护工作由C人员负责处理。&lt;SEP&gt;E客户委托C人员进行维护工作。&lt;SEP&gt;C人员为E客户提供驻点工作的维护和调整服务。</data>
