<edge source="A人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人员, B客户) refers to a relationship where A人员 provides various maintenance services and supports the operational needs of B客户. A人员 undertakes responsibilities such as handling maintenance tasks, documenting them, and ensuring the smooth functioning of B客户的 system. The organization B客户 receives comprehensive maintenance support from A人员, who is involved in both the technical and administrative aspects of maintaining B客户的 systems and operations.

A人员 not only performs maintenance work but also ensures that all necessary documentation is completed to maintain a clear record of activities carried out for B客户. This relationship emphasizes the ongoing collaboration between A人员 and B客户, highlighting the importance of continuous support and maintenance services provided by A人员 to ensure optimal performance and reliability for B客户的 systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A personnel provides technical support and maintenance services for B客户.</data>
  <data key="d9">documentation,engineer involvement,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance support,service provider,service provision,task execution</data>
