<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客戶, C人員) is a relation describing the interaction between a customer (B客戶) and personnel (C人員). C人員 is responsible for providing various types of maintenance and technical support services to B客戶. This includes addressing specific issues such as hard disk space overload and data synchronization problems. Additionally, C人員 is involved in documenting work related to the maintenance and service provision. The duties encompass both direct maintenance tasks and offering ongoing technical assistance to ensure optimal functioning and operational continuity for B客户.

C人员 also participates actively in the overall maintenance and support activities for B客戶, indicating a comprehensive role that extends beyond just immediate issue resolution to include preventative measures and continuous improvement efforts. This relationship underscores the importance of C人員's role in sustaining and enhancing the customer experience through dedicated service and proactive problem-solving approaches.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员assists in coordinating tasks related to B客户的maintenance activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">collaboration,documentation,engineer involvement,engineering service,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,responsibility,task coordination,task execution,technical support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942b136689124792272bc32a2898842c</data>
