<edge source="Splunk Enterprise 9.3.8" target="E Customer">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(E Customer, Splunk Enterprise 9.3.8) refers to the usage of Splunk Enterprise version 9.3.8 by a specific entity known as "E customer". This particular version is currently in use and serves as the primary software for their operations. However, it has been noted that the E customer needs maintenance and adjustments to ensure optimal performance. Additionally, the version is nearing its average usage threshold and approaching the end of its lifecycle, suggesting a recommendation for an upgrade to enhance both performance and security. The current status indicates that while Splunk Enterprise 9.3.8 is operational, there are ongoing requirements for updates and improvements due to these limitations.&lt;SEP&gt;The E customer is using Splunk Enterprise 9.3.8 and requires maintenance activities.&lt;SEP&gt;E customer is using the current version of Splunk Enterprise which is 9.3.8.</data>
