<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) refers to a relationship where B人员 (personnel member) provides maintenance and support services for C客户 (customer). Specifically, B人员 is responsible for handling the system maintenance work of C客户的系统 (C customer's system), which includes conducting regular maintenance tasks as well as performing updates when necessary. This role involves recording maintenance activities and ensuring that the systems remain operational and up-to-date. For example, B人员 conducted maintenance work on 2026/01/05 and provided services in December 2025. Additionally, B人员 is continuously engaged in providing maintenance services for C客户 to ensure their system remains functional and secure.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员也参与了对C客户的系统维护工作。</data>
